# Root build-context ignore. Only consulted by builds whose context IS the repo
# root (the all-in-one edge + centre-admin images). The public/* and zuup-os
# image builds use their own narrower contexts and are unaffected.
#
# The repo carries a full committed Linux kernel source tree under
# private/zuup-os/image-build/out — gigabytes that must never enter a context.
.git
.gitignore
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/out
**/*.img
**/*.iso
**/*.log

# Other apps not needed by the all-in-one root-context images.
public
private/zuup-os
private/exam-terminal
private/hardware
private/lockdown-client
memory
